---
source: tests/cli.rs
expression: help
---
Validate and manage the stored Venmo bearer token

Usage: auth <COMMAND>

Commands:
  login           Authenticate with a trusted device and password/SMS OTP, or import a bearer token
  reauthenticate  Replace an expired token using the stored trusted device and password/SMS OTP
  logout          Remove the locally stored credential
  status          Validate the credential and show the active account
  help            Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -h, --help
          Print help
